<p class="trans-verified-button-small" dir="ltr"><strong><span class="" lang="en"><span class="" lang="en"><span title="ウェブサイト管理人「そらみん。」です。
"><span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="en"><span class="">The last article was from here.</span></span></span></span></span> </strong></p>
<p dir="ltr"><strong><iframe class="embed-card embed-blogcard" style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 190px; max-width: 500px; margin: 10px 0px;" title=" (English) Spring Trigger [1] - すかいみん。" src="https://hatenablog-parts.com/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fskymin.hatenablog.com%2Fentry%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F_%2528English%2529_Spring_Trigger_%255B1%255D" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe><cite class="hatena-citation"><a href="http://skymin.hatenablog.com/entry/2018/04/26/_%28English%29_Spring_Trigger_%5B1%5D">skymin.hatenablog.com</a></cite></strong><strong> </strong></p>
<p dir="ltr"><strong> </strong></p>
<p dir="ltr"> </p>
