    ">"It's your own foot and intuition, is not it?"<br />    </span><span title="「むぅ、それボクの台詞」
    ">"Muu, it's my line"<br />    </span><span title="　不機嫌に頬を膨らませて、明智は腕を組む。
    ">My cheeks are inflated crankily, Akechi's arms.<br />    </span><span title="「まあいいや。じゃ、ボクの権限が届かない場所――　学校内の情報を探るよ」">"Well, OK, where I do not get the authority - I will explore the information in the school"</span></span></div>
<div id="gt-res-tools"> </div>
<div>Spring Trigger [2] End.</div>
